  <ifrs:DisclosureOfSummaryOfSignificantAccountingPoliciesExplanatory contextRef="Context_Duration_P1201903P">Ver detalle en las notas XBRL 800500 y 810000</ifrs:DisclosureOfSummaryOfSignificantAccountingPoliciesExplanatory>
